            <title>1.6.7</title>
            <pubDate>Tue, 07 Apr 2026 22:02:53 +0900</pubDate>
            <link>https://github.com/Saqoosha/Canopy</link>
            <sparkle:version>24</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.6.7</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>15.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[### Bug Fixes
- Fixed menu commands (Back to Launcher, Open Folder) targeting the wrong window in multi-window/tab setups by replacing custom notification tracking with SwiftUI's native @FocusedValue mechanism
- Fixed context usage bar calculation to match the Claude Code extension's pie chart formula by accounting for max output tokens
]]></description>
