            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>15.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[### Changes
- Add hardened runtime entitlements for camera, microphone, AppleScript, contacts, calendars, location, photos library, reminders, and speech recognition
- CLI processes spawned within Canopy can now properly trigger macOS TCC permission dialogs when accessing protected resources
]]></description>
